# admin data store
# data/leads.json and data/clients.json are committed as empty seeds ([]).
# Netlify serverless containers are ephemeral — production writes do not persist
# across deploys. Use GET /api/admin/export to download a backup periodically.
# To prevent accidentally committing live data locally, you can run:
#   git update-index --assume-unchanged data/leads.json data/clients.json
